{{Vgname|俠盜獵車手IV|en=Grand Theft Auto IV}}是「[[俠盜獵車手系列|俠盜獵車手系列]]」第十一個作品，也是《侠盗猎车手》系列HD时代的首部作品。Rockstar Games原定遊戲在2007年10月16日於[[PlayStation_3|PlayStation 3]]和[[Xbox_360|Xbox 360]]平台上推出，但因[[Playstation_3|Playstation 3]]版開發不順导致发售日期延後到2008年4月29日。遊戲使用全新的[[RAGE引擎|RAGE引擎]]<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.mtv.com/news/articles/1530131/20060503/index.jhtml|title=The First Rule Of Ping-Pong Club: Talk About Rockstar's Table Tennis Game|date=2006-05-03|author=Stephen Totilo|publisher=MTV|accessdate=2015-09-08|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/65YLebxgt?url=http://www.mtv.com/news/articles/1530131/rockstar-games-hosts-table-tennis-battles.jhtml|archive-date=2012-02-18|dead-url=no}}</ref>。而[[Windows|Windows]]平台則於12月2日於北美發售。[[Xbox_360|Xbox 360]]平台上有兩個獨立的[[資料片|資料片]]，第一部為《[[俠盜獵車手：失落與詛咒|俠盜獵車手：失落與詛咒]]》，第二部為《[[俠盜獵車手：夜生活之曲|俠盜獵車手：夜生活之曲]]》，分别在2009年2月17日和10月29日釋出。在2010年初，官方宣佈Xbox 360上的兩部資料片將以「[[俠盜獵車手：自由城之章|自由城之章]]」為名，移植至PC與PS3平臺<ref>{{cite web| url = http://www.rockstargames.com/newswire/article/4061/| title = Episodes from Liberty City Now Coming to PlayStation 3 and PC this April|author=R.Q |publisher=Rockstargames |date=2010-03-18 |accessdate=2015-09-08}}</ref>，同年4月13日美版發售，4月16日歐版發售。於2017年2月9日開始向下相容於[[Xbox_One|Xbox One]]。

作为一个成功的游戏，侠盗猎车手IV在一周内的销售额达到了5亿美金。<ref>{{cite web| url = http://www.boston.com/business/articles/2008/05/07/take_twos_grand_theft_auto_iv_tops_500m_in_1st_week_sales/| title = "Take-Two's 'Grand Theft Auto IV' tops $500M in week 1 sales"| author = | publisher = Boston| date = 2008-05-07| access-date = 2009-03-28| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20080517105905/http://www.boston.com/business/articles/2008/05/07/take_twos_grand_theft_auto_iv_tops_500m_in_1st_week_sales| archive-date = 2008-05-17| dead-url = no}}</ref>游戏媒体IGN对这款游戏评价非常高，声称它是[[電子遊戲歷史|電子遊戲歷史]]上自《[[塞尔达传说：时之笛|塞尔达传说：时之笛]]》以来最好的游戏<ref>{{cite news | author=Hilary Goldstein | title=Grand Theft Auto IV Review | date=2008-04-28 | publisher=IGN | url=http://xbox360.ign.com/articles/869/869381p2.html | work= | pages= | accessdate=2008-04-28 | language= | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080429014003/http://xbox360.ign.com/articles/869/869381p2.html | archive-date=2008-04-29 | dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref name="GameSpot Review">{{cite web |url=http://www.gamespot.com/reviews/grand-theft-auto-iv-review/1900-6190027/ |title=Grand Theft Auto IV Review for Xbox 360 |last=Calvert |first=Justin |work=[[GameSpot|GameSpot]] |publisher=[[CBS_Interactive|CBS Interactive]] |date=2008-04-28 |accessdate=2014-01-19 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6SZTNL4rW?url=http://www.gamespot.com/reviews/grand-theft-auto-iv-review/1900-6190027/ |archivedate=2014-09-14 |deadurl=no }}{{cite web |url=http://www.gamespot.com/reviews/grand-theft-auto-iv-review/1900-6190025/ |title=Grand Theft Auto IV Review for PS3 |last=Calvert |first=Justin |work=[[GameSpot|GameSpot]] |publisher=[[CBS_Interactive|CBS Interactive]] |date=2008-04-28 |accessdate=2014-01-19 |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/6SZTRmn5Z?url=http://www.gamespot.com/reviews/grand-theft-auto-iv-review/1900-6190025/ |archivedate=2014-09-14 |deadurl=no }}</ref>。

