微软公司互动娱乐事业部副总裁[[彼得·摩尔|彼得·摩尔]]（Peter Moore）在2006年的E3展公布，游戏将发布于Xbox 360平台上，并卷起他的袖子露出了侠盗猎车手IV标志的临时纹身。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://ign.com/articles/2006/05/09/e3-2006-grand-theft-auto-iv-announced |title=E3 2006: Grand Theft Auto IV Announced |last=Sanders |first=Kathleen |publisher=[[IGN|IGN]]. [[Ziff_Davis|Ziff Davis]] |date=2006-05-09 |accessdate=2014-12-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151005165034/http://www.ign.com/articles/2006/05/09/e3-2006-grand-theft-auto-iv-announced |archive-date=2015-10-05 |dead-url=no }}</ref>Rockstar Games开始声称游戏的发售日期为2007年10月16日，然而投资银行Wedbush Morgan的分析师{{link-en|迈克尔·帕切特|Michael Pachter}}（Michael Pachter）认为Take-Two公司可能将游戏推迟到2008年以稳住其财务业绩，并避免与其它备受瞩目的游戏，如[[光晕3|光晕3]]竞争。<ref>{{cite web|last=Gibson|first=Ellie|date=2007-06-04|url=http://www.gamesindustry.biz/articles/pachter-predicts-delay-for-gta-iv|title=Pachter predicts delay for GTA IV|publisher=[[Gamesindustry.biz|Gamesindustry.biz]]|accessdate=2007-04-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080411013411/http://www.gamesindustry.biz/articles/pachter-predicts-delay-for-gta-iv|archive-date=2008-04-11|dead-url=no}}</ref>对此Rockstar回应说，游戏仍将在“十月下旬”发布。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://archive.videogamesdaily.com/news/200706/004.asp |title=Rockstar Dimisses Talk of GTA IV Delay |last=Wollenschlaeger |first=Alex |publisher=''Kikizo'' |date=2007-06-04 |accessdate=2007-06-07 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110510053239/http://archive.videogamesdaily.com/news/200706/004.asp |archivedate=2011-05-10 }}</ref>2007年8月2日，Take-Two公司宣布游戏[[跳票|跳票]]，并会延迟公司的第二个财政季度（2008年2月至4月）<ref name="ttpress">{{cite press release |title=Launch of Grand Theft Auto IV Now Planned for Fiscal 2008 |publisher=[[Take-Two_Interactive|Take-Two Interactive]] |date=2007-08-02 |url=http://ir.take2games.com/External.File?t=2&item=g7rqBLVLuv81UAmrh20Mp/u4L3W2FHQzV8W%20X201IQFocoNVSFW9tkIaVK0BgSX6bOSJ65iqAfU3QDZOLsTijA== |accessdate=2007-08-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180919083117/http://ir.take2games.com/External.File?t=2&item=g7rqBLVLuv81UAmrh20Mp%2Fu4L3W2FHQzV8W%20X201IQFocoNVSFW9tkIaVK0BgSX6bOSJ65iqAfU3QDZOLsTijA%3D%3D |archive-date=2018-09-19 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>在与投资者们的电话会议上，Take-Two公司的的斯特劳斯·泽尔尼克（Strauss Zelnick）归咎于延迟是“几乎严重的技术问题......不用担心，但要考虑挑战。”<ref>{{cite web |last=McWhertor |first=Michael |title=Take-Two Execs Explain GTA IV Delay |publisher=Kotaku |date=2007-08-02 |url=http://www.kotaku.com.au/2007/08/taketwo_interactive_taketwo_ex/ |accessdate=2007-08-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131217224636/http://www.kotaku.com.au/2007/08/taketwo_interactive_taketwo_ex/ |archive-date=2013-12-17 |dead-url=no }}</ref>据透露，随着在PlayStation 3版本的某些游戏技术难题以及Xbox 360版本上的存储问题促使了这次延迟。<ref name="MTV">{{cite press release |title=Grand Theft Auto IV Developer Announces Release Date, Says Whether There Will Be Another Hot Coffee |last=Totilo |first=Stephen |publisher=MTV |date=2008-01-24 |accessdate=2013-09-27 |url=http://www.mtv.com/news/articles/1580161/20080123/index.jhtml |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100421170156/http://www.mtv.com/news/articles/1580161/20080123/index.jhtml |archive-date=2010-04-21 |dead-url=no }}</ref>2008年1月24日，Take-Two公司宣布，游戏将在2008年4月29日发布。<ref name="ReleaseDate" />随着发布日期的临近，Rockstar Games及其母公司Take-Two开始花巨资，通过各种形式，包括电视广告，网络视频，广告牌，病毒式营销以及重新设计的网站来宣传即将到来的侠盗猎车手IV。还发布了两个在PlayStation 3平台和Xbox 360平台的游戏特别版。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://au.ign.com/articles/2007/06/27/grand-theft-auto-iv-special-edition-contents-revealed |title=Grand Theft Auto IV Special Edition Contents Revealed |last=Ring |first=Bennett |publisher=IGN |date=2007-06-26 |accessdate=2013-09-27 |archive-url=https://archive.is/20130926150129/http://au.ign.com/articles/2007/06/27/grand-theft-auto-iv-special-edition-contents-revealed |archive-date=2013-09-26 |dead-url=no }}</ref>2008年4月18日，在Take-Two公司的一次股东大会上，首席执行官本·费德（Ben Feder）宣布，侠盗猎车手IV已经成功“[[摘走了金牌|摘走了金牌]]（gone gold）”、“已经生产并运输到零售商手里了（in production and in trucks en route to retailers）”。<ref name="gold">{{cite web |url=http://www.gamespot.com/articles/grand-theft-auto-iv-golden-already-in-transit/1100-6189477/ |title=Grand Theft Auto IV golden, already in transit |last=Magrino |first=Tom |date=2008-04-18 |accessdate=2013-09-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140302132836/http://www.gamespot.com/articles/grand-theft-auto-iv-golden-already-in-transit/1100-6189477/ |archive-date=2014-03-02 |dead-url=no }}</ref>游戏最终于欧洲，北美洲和大洋洲2008年4月29日，日本2008年10月30日在PlayStation3和Xbox360平台上发布了，<ref name="ReleaseDate">{{cite web |url=http://ir.take2games.com/phoenix.zhtml?c=86428&p=irol-newsArticle_print&ID=1099620&highlight= |title=Take-Two Interactive Software — Investor Relations — Take-Two News Release |publisher=[[Take-Two_Interactive|Take-Two Interactive]] |accessdate=2010-10-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180725112512/http://ir.take2games.com/phoenix.zhtml?c=86428&p=irol-newsArticle_print&ID=1099620&highlight= |archive-date=2018-07-25 |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://kotaku.com/5037364/gtaiv-dated-for-japan|title=GTAIV Dated for Japan|last=Ashcraft|first=Brian|date=2008-08-15|publisher=Kotaku|accessdate=2008-11-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20081210090414/http://kotaku.com/5037364/gtaiv-dated-for-japan|archive-date=2008-12-10|dead-url=no}}</ref>总体而言，侠盗猎车手IV的开发人员将近1000人，并花费超过三年半的时间完工，估计总成本约1亿美元，使得它在当时成为有史以来开发的最昂贵的电子游戏。<ref name="cost">{{cite web|url=http://www.gamesindustry.biz/articles/gta-iv-most-expensive-game-ever-developed|title=GTA IV: Most Expensive Game Ever Developed?|last=Androvich|first=Mark|date=2008-04-30|accessdate=2008-05-01|publisher=[[GamesIndustry.biz|GamesIndustry.biz]]|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101231145617/http://www.gamesindustry.biz/articles/gta-iv-most-expensive-game-ever-developed|archive-date=2010-12-31|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2008年6月8日，[[Rockstar_North|Rockstar North]]及[[Rockstar_Toronto|Rockstar Toronto]]宣布制作发售侠盗猎车手IV的Windows版本。<ref name="gta4pchan-IGNUK">{{cite web|url=http://uk.ign.com/articles/2008/10/30/grand-theft-auto-iv-uk-hands-on|title=Grand Theft Auto IV UK Hands-on|last=Robinson|first=Martin|date=2008-10-30|publisher=IGN|accessdate=2008-10-30|archive-date=2019-12-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191202182302/https://uk.ign.com/articles/2008/10/30/grand-theft-auto-iv-uk-hands-on}}</ref><ref name="PCRelease-Take2">{{cite press release|url=http://ir.take2games.com/phoenix.zhtml?c=86428&p=irol-newsArticle&ID=1487915|title=Rockstar Games Announces Grand Theft Auto IV for the PC|publisher=[[Take-Two_Interactive|Take-Two Interactive]]|date=2008-08-06|accessdate=2008-08-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180919083237/http://ir.take2games.com/phoenix.zhtml?c=86428&p=irol-newsArticle&ID=1487915|archive-date=2018-09-19|dead-url=no}}</ref>游戏最初公布于将于北美2008年11月18日，欧洲2008年11月21日发布，但后来都被分别被推迟到2008年12月2日与3日。<ref name="PCRelease-Take2" />此版本包括主机板没有的扩展功能，<ref name="PCRelease-Take2"/>包括交通密度控制，配置绘制距离和重播编辑器（Replay Editor）。<ref name="PC features"/>重播编辑器让玩家录制和编辑的游戏视频剪辑，上传至Rockstar社交俱乐部（Rockstar's Social Club）网站。通过{{link-en|Games for Windows - Live|Games for Windows – Live}}进行在线播放。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://ign.com/articles/2008/09/22/gfw-celebrates-two-year-anniversary |title=GFW Celebrates Two-Year Anniversary |last=Thang |first=Jimmy |publisher=[[IGN|IGN]]. [[Ziff_Davis|Ziff Davis]] |date=2008-09-22 |accessdate=2008-09-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121108162757/http://www.ign.com/articles/2008/09/22/gfw-celebrates-two-year-anniversary |archive-date=2012-11-08 |dead-url=no }}</ref>Windows版本也支持多达32名玩家同时在线的多人模式。<ref name="GameSpot PC Review"/>光碟被[[SecuROM|SecuROM]]保护，只有通过在线激活才能正常运行游戏。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://ign.com/articles/2008/11/28/rockstar-talks-gta-iv-pc-drm?page=2 |title=Rockstar Talks GTA IV PC DRM |page=2 |author=IGN Staff |publisher=[[IGN|IGN]]. [[Ziff_Davis|Ziff Davis]] |date=2008-11-28 |accessdate=2008-11-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130927195508/http://www.ign.com/articles/2008/11/28/rockstar-talks-gta-iv-pc-drm?page=2 |archive-date=2013-09-27 |dead-url=no }}</ref>该游戏于2009年1月4日在[[Steam|Steam]]上线。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://store.steampowered.com/news/1395 |title=Rockstar Games Brings Full Line-up to Steam |author=[[Steam_(software)|Steam]] |publisher=[[Valve_Corporation|Valve Corporation]] |date=2008-01-04 |accessdate=2010-10-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100820162759/http://store.steampowered.com/news/1395 |archive-date=2010-08-20 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

