当侠盗猎车手IV于2008年12月发布[[Microsoft_Windows|Microsoft Windows]]版本时，得到了如潮好评。[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]计算的平均得分为90/100，根据40条评论总结为“普遍好评（universal acclaim）”。<ref name="MCPC"/>[[GameRankings|GameRankings]]据40条评论给予88％的平均得分。<ref name="GRPC"/>评论家称赞游戏增强的视觉效果<ref name="CVG PC Review"/><ref name="VideoGamer.com PC Review"/><ref name="GameZone PC Review"/>及画面，<ref name="GameSpot PC Review"/><ref name="1UP PC Review"/><ref name="IGN PC Review"/><ref name="GameZone PC Review"/>并批评家用机版本此方面的不足。<ref name="1UP PC Review"/><ref name="Eurogamer PC Review"/><ref name="IGN PC Review"/>

游戏中一些新功能，<ref name="IGN PC Review"/><ref name="GameZone PC Review"/>如新增的视频编辑器也得到了好评，Gamespot的卡尔弗特（Calvert）称它是“一个伟大的创作方式（a great way to get creative）”，<ref name="GameSpot PC Review"/>然而[[Eurogamer|Eurogamer]]的基隆·吉伦（Kieron Gillen ）却指出编辑器不能预测时间，<ref name="Eurogamer PC Review"/>评论家也赞扬了游戏的自定义电台，可以让玩家听自己选择的音乐；[[1UP.com|1UP.com]]的汤姆·奇克（Tom Chick）称这是此平台最好的功能，<ref name="1UP PC Review"/>[[GameZone|GameZone]]的史蒂芬·霍珀（Steven Hopper）声称“触动很大（great touch）”<ref name="GameZone PC Review">{{cite web |url=http://pc.gamezone.com/gzreviews/r29676.htm |title=Grand Theft Auto IV Review – PC |last=Hopper |first=Steven |publisher=[[GameZone|GameZone]] |date=2008-12-08 |accessdate=2010-12-23 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090308013926/http://pc.gamezone.com/gzreviews/r29676.htm |archivedate=2009-03-08 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>平台的升级使多人联机模式相对于家用机版的16名玩家翻了一倍（32名玩家），也遇到了正反馈；Eurogamer的吉伦说，“可能会有点儿混乱...（possibility for mayhem... increases）”，<ref name="Eurogamer PC Review"/>而GameSpy的威尔·塔特尔（Will Tuttle）认为丰富了玩家的“应变能力”。<ref name="GameSpy PC Review"/>

此平台的增强视觉效果被许多评论家赞扬。<ref name="GameZone PC Review"/>[[电脑与电子游戏|电脑与电子游戏]]杂志的安迪·鲁宾逊（Andy Robinson）称视觉效果“令人印象深刻”，<ref name="CVG PC Review"/>而[[VideoGamer.com|VideoGamer.com]]的汤姆·奥利称之“精湛（superb）”。<ref name="VideoGamer.com PC Review"/>相反，该游戏的系统配置要求，有人认为难以开启高级视觉设置运行，<ref name="GameSpot PC Review"/>因而备受批评。<ref name="IGN PC Review"/><ref name="VideoGamer.com PC Review"/>Eurogamer的吉伦说，尽管Windows版本是“最吸引人的版本（the most attractive version）”，然而这样高的配置要求“令人望而却步（annoyingly fiddly to get there）”。<ref name="Eurogamer PC Review"/>GameSpy的塔特尔表示，可以忽视换取游戏中其他功能的苛刻的系统要求。<ref name="GameSpy PC Review"/>

== 销售 ==
在最初的24小时内，侠盗猎车手IV便售出了360万套，获得了大约3.1亿美元的收入。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.v3.co.uk/v3-uk/news/1972265/gta-iv-smashes-sales-records |title=GTA IV smashes sales records |last=Nichols |first=Shaun |publisher=V3 |date=2008-05-09 |accessdate=2008-05-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141108021154/http://www.v3.co.uk/v3-uk/news/1972265/gta-iv-smashes-sales-records |archive-date=2014-11-08 |dead-url=no }}</ref>一周之内，它在全球范围内产生的收入超过5亿美元，等同于为Take Two售出约600万套。<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.nytimes.com/2008/05/07/technology/07game.html |title=A $500 Million Week for Grand Theft Auto |last=Richtel |first=Mike |work=[[The_New_York_Times|The New York Times]] |publisher=[[Arthur_Ochs_Sulzberger,_Jr.|Arthur Ochs Sulzberger, Jr.]] |date=2008-05-07 |accessdate=2008-05-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110512055157/http://www.nytimes.com/2008/05/07/technology/07game.html |archive-date=2011-05-12 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.reuters.com/article/2008/05/07/us-grandtheftauto-sales-idUSWNAS233520080507 |title=Take-Two's Grand Theft Auto 4 sales top $500 million |last=Paul |first=Franklin |publisher=''[[Reuters|Reuters]]'' |date=2008-05-07 |accessdate=2008-05-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110604180450/http://www.reuters.com/article/2008/05/07/us-grandtheftauto-sales-idUSWNAS233520080507 |archive-date=2011-06-04 |dead-url=no }}</ref>{{注|1=本游戏第一个星期的销售记录击败了便打破了[[光环3|光环3]]（3.2亿美元）的记录。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.dailytelegraph.com.au/grand-theft-auto-iv-smashes-all-sales-records/story-e6freuy9-1111116285070 |title=Grand Theft Auto IV smashes all sales records |last=Fenech |first=Stephen |publisher=''[[The_Daily_Telegraph|The Daily Telegraph]]'' |date=2008-05-09 |accessdate=2014-06-15 |archive-date=2020-09-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200927183458/https://www.dailytelegraph.com.au/grand-theft-auto-iv-smashes-all-sales-records/news-story/8f94cd9ecd5362682e77d3558e03c75d?nk=e8590ab8bf4458d7dcd4d7e6bbcca04d-1601231698 |dead-url=no }}</ref>}}销售的数额甚至超过了预期。<ref name="shares rise">{{Cite news |url=http://www.reuters.com/article/2008/04/28/businesspro-grandtheftauto-dc-idUKN2116666620080428 |title=Take-Two shares rise amid rave reviews for GTA4 |accessdate=2011-10-06 |last=Hillis |first=Scott |date=2008-04-28 |publisher=Reuters |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121023121948/http://www.reuters.com/article/2008/04/28/businesspro-grandtheftauto-dc-idUKN2116666620080428 |archive-date=2012-10-23 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="richtel">{{cite news |url=http://www.nytimes.com/2008/04/29/technology/29game.html |title=For Gamers, the Craving Won't Quit |accessdate=2008-04-29 |last=Richtel |first=Matt |date=2008-04-29 |work=[[The_New_York_Times|The New York Times]] |publisher=[[Arthur_Ochs_Sulzberger,_Jr.|Arthur Ochs Sulzberger, Jr.]] |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20081209035721/http://www.nytimes.com/2008/04/29/technology/29game.html |archive-date=2008-12-09 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="big or huge">{{cite web |url=http://www.gamespot.com/articles/qanda-gtaiv-big-or-huge/1100-6190011/ |title=Q&A: GTAIV – Big or huge? |accessdate=2008-04-28 |last=Magrino |first=Tom |date=2008-04-28 |publisher=[[GameSpot|GameSpot]] |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140301140316/http://www.gamespot.com/articles/qanda-gtaiv-big-or-huge/1100-6190011/ |archive-date=2014-03-01 |dead-url=no }}</ref>一个月后，游戏已经售出超过850万套了。<ref>{{cite press release |url=http://ir.take2games.com/phoenix.zhtml?c=86428&p=irol-newsArticle&ID=1163124 |title=Take-Two Interactive Software, Inc. Reports Strong Second Quarter Fiscal 2008 Financial Results |publisher=[[Take-Two_Interactive|Take-Two Interactive]] |date=2008-06-05 |accessdate=2008-06-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180919083105/http://ir.take2games.com/phoenix.zhtml?c=86428&p=irol-newsArticle&ID=1163124 |archive-date=2018-09-19 |dead-url=no }}</ref>它于2008年5月13日立下了三项[[吉尼斯世界纪录|吉尼斯世界纪录]]：24小时内销售额最高的电子游戏，24小时内销售额最高的娱乐产品，24小时内最畅销的电子游戏，<ref>{{cite web |url=http://gamers.guinnessworldrecords.com/news/130508_GTA_IV_break_record.aspx |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20101223211049/http://gamers.guinnessworldrecords.com/news/130508_GTA_IV_break_record.aspx |archivedate=2010-12-23 |title=Confirmed: Grand Theft Auto IV Breaks Guinness World Records With Biggest Entertainment Release Of All-Time |accessdate=2008-05-13 |date=2008-05-13 |work=[[Guinness_World_Records|Guinness World Records]] |publisher=[[Jim_Pattison_Group|Jim Pattison Group]] |deadurl=yes }}</ref>之後这三项纪录皆被[[侠盗猎车手V|侠盗猎车手V]]所打破。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.polygon.com/2013/10/9/4819272/grand-theft-auto-5-smashes-7-guinness-world-records |title=Grand Theft Auto 5 smashes 7 Guinness World Records |last=Pitcher |first=Jenna |publisher=[[Polygon_(website)|Polygon]] |date=2013-10-09 |accessdate=2014-06-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131009080632/http://www.polygon.com/2013/10/9/4819272/grand-theft-auto-5-smashes-7-guinness-world-records |archive-date=2013-10-09 |dead-url=no }}</ref>2011年3月11日，Take-Two公司宣布，游戏已经售出超过2000万套，當時整个侠盗猎车手系列加總已卖出一亿套。<ref name="TakeTwo2011March">{{cite press release |url=http://www.vg247.com/2011/03/10/take-two-drops-franchise-figures-gta-iv-sells-20-million-bioshock-series-at-8-million |title=Take-Two: GTA IV hits 20m, BioShock series at 8m |publisher=[[Take-Two_Interactive|Take-Two Interactive]] |date=2011-03-10 |accessdate=2011-03-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110313023405/http://www.vg247.com/2011/03/10/take-two-drops-franchise-figures-gta-iv-sells-20-million-bioshock-series-at-8-million/ |archive-date=2011-03-13 |dead-url=no }}</ref>截至2013年7月，游戏已经售出超过2500万套。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.gameinformer.com/b/news/archive/2013/07/30/grand-theft-auto-iv-has-sold-25-million-units-to_2d00_date.aspx |title=Grand Theft Auto IV Has Sold 25 Million Units To-Date |last=Futter |first=Mike |publisher=''[[GameInformer|GameInformer]]'' |date=2013-07-30 |accessdate=2014-06-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151208200012/http://www.gameinformer.com/b/news/archive/2013/07/30/grand-theft-auto-iv-has-sold-25-million-units-to_2d00_date.aspx |archive-date=2015-12-08 |dead-url=no }}</ref>其系列作中首位的销售量直到后继者[[侠盗猎车手V|侠盗猎车手V]]发布后才被打破。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://ign.com/articles/2013/09/20/gta-5-sales-hit-1-billion-in-three-days |title=GTA 5 Sales Hit $1 Billion in Three Days |last=Goldfarb |first=Andrew |publisher=[[IGN|IGN]]. [[Ziff_Davis|Ziff Davis]] |date=2013-09-20 |accessdate=2014-12-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141208234930/http://www.ign.com/articles/2013/09/20/gta-5-sales-hit-1-billion-in-three-days |archive-date=2014-12-08 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

在英国，本作成为了有史以来销售最快的游戏，24小时内销售超过631000套。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.mcvuk.com/news/read/uk-charts-all-conquering-gta-iv-hits-no-1 |last=Ingham |first=Tim |title=UK CHARTS: All-conquering GTA IV hits No.1 |date=2008-05-06 |publisher=[[Market_for_Home_Computing_and_Video_Games|Market for Home Computing and Video Games]] |accessdate=2008-05-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131104235150/http://www.mcvuk.com/news/read/uk-charts-all-conquering-gta-iv-hits-no-1 |archive-date=2013-11-04 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="UKfirstdaysales">{{cite web |title=GTA IV smashes day one sales record |last=Ingham |first=Tim |publisher=[[Market_for_Home_Computing_and_Video_Games|Market for Home Computing and Video Games]] |url=http://www.mcvuk.com/news/read/gta-iv-smashes-day-one-sales-record |date=2008-04-30 |accessdate=2008-05-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110814233255/http://www.mcvuk.com/news/read/gta-iv-smashes-day-one-sales-record |archive-date=2011-08-14 |dead-url=no }}</ref>打破了同一时期[[侠盗猎车手：圣安地列斯|侠盗猎车手：圣安地列斯]]（501,000套）的记录。<ref>{{cite news |url=http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/1915219/Grand-Theft-Auto-IV-becomes-UKs-fastest-selling-game.html |title=Grand Theft Auto IV is fastest-selling game |accessdate=2008-05-01 |last=Beaumont |first=Claudine |date=2008-05-01 |publisher=''[[The_Daily_Telegraph|The Daily Telegraph]]'' |location=London |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090202050928/http://www.telegraph.co.uk/news/1915219/Grand-Theft-Auto-IV-becomes-UKs-fastest-selling-game.html |archive-date=2009-02-02 |dead-url=no }}</ref>发售五天后，游戏便在英国有927,000套的销量。<ref name="UKfirstweeksales">{{cite web |url=http://www.gamesindustry.biz/articles/gta-iv-926-000-copies-sold-in-five-days |last=Androvich |first=Mark |title=GTA IV: 926,000 copies sold in five days |date=2008-05-06 |publisher=[[GamesIndustry.biz|GamesIndustry.biz]] |accessdate=2008-05-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170315184517/http://www.gamesindustry.biz/articles/gta-iv-926-000-copies-sold-in-five-days |archive-date=2017-03-15 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.mcvuk.com/news/read/360-outselling-ps3-in-gta-software-battle |last=Ingham |first=Tim |title=360 outselling PS3 in GTA software 'battle' |date=2008-05-06 |publisher=[[Market_for_Home_Computing_and_Video_Games|Market for Home Computing and Video Games]] |accessdate=2008-05-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131105000711/http://www.mcvuk.com/news/read/360-outselling-ps3-in-gta-software-battle |archive-date=2013-11-05 |dead-url=no }}</ref>而在同一时期的美国，已经销售了285万套了。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.gamespot.com/articles/npd-us-april-game-revs-spike-on-gtaiv/1100-6191066/ |last=Sinclair |first=Brendan |title=NPD: US game revs spike on 2.85M GTAIVs |date=2008-05-15 |publisher=[[GameSpot|GameSpot]] |accessdate=2008-05-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140301133233/http://www.gamespot.com/articles/npd-us-april-game-revs-spike-on-gtaiv/1100-6191066/ |archive-date=2014-03-01 |dead-url=no }}</ref>2008年底，在美国便销售了518万套了。<ref name="gamedaily">{{cite web |title=NPD: Nintendo Drives '08 Industry Sales Past $21 Billion |url=http://www.gamedaily.com/articles/news/npd-nintendo-drives-08-industry-sales-past-21-billion-/?biz=1 |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090331111632/http://www.gamedaily.com/articles/news/npd-nintendo-drives-08-industry-sales-past-21-billion-/?biz=1 |archivedate=2009-03-31 |publisher=[[Game_Daily|Game Daily]] |accessdate=2009-01-15 |date=2009-01-15 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>日本[[Media_Create|Media Create]]报道，游戏发售前5天，在日本PlayStation 3与Xbox 360上便分别卖出了133000套与34000套。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://kotaku.com/5078486/grand-theft-auto-iv-1-with-a-bullet-in-japan |title=Grand Theft Auto IV #1 With A Bullet In Japan |last=McWhertor |first=Michael |date=2008-11-06 |publisher=Kotaku |accessdate=2008-11-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20081109061005/http://kotaku.com/5078486/grand-theft-auto-iv-1-with-a-bullet-in-japan |archive-date=2008-11-09 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

=== 特別版 ===
官方在2007年5月21日宣佈將推出「俠盜獵車手IV特別版」（{{lang|en|Grand Theft Auto IV Special Edition}}）<ref>{{cite web |url=http://ir.take2games.com/ReleaseDetail.cfm?ReleaseID=244729 |title=Rockstar Games announces Grand Theft Auto IV Special Edition |access-date=2007-06-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070524032018/http://ir.take2games.com/ReleaseDetail.cfm?ReleaseID=244729 |archive-date=2007-05-24 |dead-url=yes }}{{en}}</ref>，這個特別版將會被放在一個[[金屬|金屬]][[保險箱|保險箱]]內，並會包含：

* 一個用於該[[金屬|金屬]][[保險箱|保險箱]]的[[鎖匙|鎖匙]]和[[鎖匙扣|鎖匙扣]]
* 一個限量版Rockstar[[旅行袋|旅行袋]]
* 一個包含從未公開的美術作品的「Grand Theft Auto IV Art Book」
* 遊戲原聲[[CD|CD]]（只在此特別版發售）
* 一個特別包裝的[[PS3|PS3]]或[[Xbox_360|Xbox 360]]遊戲光碟

在[[美國|美國]]的零售價是$89.00[[美金|美金]]，而在[[澳洲|澳洲]]的零售價是$149.95[[澳幣|澳幣]]。

== 资料片 ==
侠盗猎车手IV的两款资料片也先后发布。这两款资料片在[[Xbox_Live|Xbox Live]]是作为[[追加下载内容|追加下载内容]]（Downloadable Content，DLC）发布的，<ref>{{cite web |url=http://kotaku.com/5154447/grand-theft-auto-iv-the-lost-and-damned-review |title=Grand Theft Auto IV: The Lost And Damned Review |last=McWhertor |first=Michael |publisher=Kotaku |date=2009-02-17 |accessdate=2013-09-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131007154217/http://kotaku.com/5154447/grand-theft-auto-iv-the-lost-and-damned-review |archive-date=2013-10-07 |dead-url=no }}</ref>要求先装有原版游戏。后来它们捆绑为一个独立的游戏——[[侠盗猎车手：自由城之章|侠盗猎车手：自由城之章]]在PC平台上发布，便不需要以原版游戏基础来安装了。<ref name="announce gay tony"/>丹·豪斯（Dan Houser）表示资料片展示了“自由城的另一面（a different side of Liberty City）”。<ref name="gta4dlc">{{cite news |url = http://usatoday30.usatoday.com/tech/gaming/2008-11-19-gta-damned_N.htm |title = 'Grand Theft Auto' yields road to the 'Lost and Damned' |accessdate = 2008-11-20 |date = 2008-11-20 |publisher = ''[[USA_Today|USA Today]]'' |first = Mike |last = Snider |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20121103212838/http://usatoday30.usatoday.com/tech/gaming/2008-11-19-gta-damned_N.htm |archive-date = 2012-11-03 |dead-url = no }}</ref>

第一款资料片为[[侠盗猎车手：失落与诅咒|侠盗猎车手：失落与诅咒]]，发布于2009年2月17日，<ref>{{cite web| last = Bramwell| first = Tom| title = Rockstar prices GTAIV: Lost and Damned| publisher = [[Eurogamer|Eurogamer]]| date = 2009-01-22| url = http://www.eurogamer.net/articles/rockstar-prices-gtaiv-the-lost-and-damned| accessdate = 2009-01-22| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20090123220458/http://www.eurogamer.net/articles/rockstar-prices-gtaiv-the-lost-and-damned| archive-date = 2009-01-23| dead-url = no}}</ref>主角为强尼·克雷比兹（Johnny Klebitz），自由城飞车党“失落”（The Lost）的一员。第二款资料片为[[侠盗猎车手：夜生活之曲|侠盗猎车手：夜生活之曲]]，发布于2009年10月29日，<ref>{{cite web |last=Gibson |first=Ellie |url=http://www.eurogamer.net/articles/new-gtaiv-dlc-gets-release-date |title=New GTAIV DLC gets release date Xbox 360 News — Page 1 |publisher=[[Eurogamer|Eurogamer]] |date=2009-07-23 |accessdate=2010-10-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110514085155/http://www.eurogamer.net/articles/new-gtaiv-dlc-gets-release-date |archive-date=2011-05-14 |dead-url=no }}</ref>主角为路易斯·费尔南多·洛佩斯（Luis Fernando Lopez），夜总会老板托尼·普林斯（Tony Prince，绰号“[[同性恋|基佬]]托尼（ Gay Tony ））的助理，并跟随他帮助解决帮派，朋友，家族的冲突。<ref name="announce gay tony">{{cite web | url = http://www.shacknews.com/article/58785/second-gta-4-expansion-tells | title = Second GTA 4 Expansion Tells 'The Ballad of Gay Tony' | first = Nick | last = Breckon | date = 2009-05-26 | accessdate = 2009-05-26 | publisher = [[Shacknews|Shacknews]] | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20110614160058/http://www.shacknews.com/article/58785/second-gta-4-expansion-tells | archive-date = 2011-06-14 | dead-url = no }}</ref>

