== 争议 ==
{{Main|对侠盗猎车手IV的争议}}
=== 城市形象影响 ===
2007年3月29日，[[Rockstar|Rockstar]]官方網站推出了遊戲第一個預告片。片中出現了一些[[美國|美國]][[纽约市|纽约市]]的地標，例如[[自由神像|自由神像]]、[[時報廣場|時代廣場]]等。片中旁白說道：「人生是很複雜的，我殺過人、偷運過人、販賣過人。或許到了這裡，事情將有所不同」（{{lang|en|Life is complicated. - I killed people, smuggled people, sold people. Perhaps here, things will be different.}}），[[纽约|纽约]]市官方對遊戲選擇了[[纽约|纽约]]市作為遊戲處境感到震驚，又表示遊戲並沒有反映[[纽约|纽约]]市實際犯罪情況<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.computerandvideogames.com/article.php?id=161197 |title=New York appalled with GTA IV setting |publisher=GameRadar |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20070607000618/http://www.computerandvideogames.com/article.php?id=161197 |archivedate=2007-06-07 |accessdate=2007-06-03 }}</ref>[[纽约|纽约]]市市長[[邁克·彭博|邁克·彭博]]的發言人指：「市長不支持任何透過傷害、殺死警察，而得到點數的電子遊戲」<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.nydailynews.com/entertainment/2007/03/31/2007-03-31_pols_rage_as_vid_game_takes_shot_at_city-4.html |title=Pols rage as vid game takes shot at city |author=Ivan Pereira，Michael Saul |publisher=DAILY NEWS |date=2007-03-31 |accessdate=2015-09-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110629160529/http://www.nydailynews.com/entertainment/2007/03/31/2007-03-31_pols_rage_as_vid_game_takes_shot_at_city-4.html |archive-date=2011-06-29 |dead-url=no }}</ref>[[游戏开发者大会|國際遊戲開發者協會]]總幹事贾森·德拉罗卡（Jason Della Rocca）則批評纽约市官方虛偽，指他們只批評電子遊戲，而不是其他娛樂，例如其他以纽约為背景的書本、電影、電視節目。<ref>{{cite web| url = http://www.newsfactor.com/news/New-York-Balks-at-Grand-Theft-Auto/story.xhtml?story_id=0300003HXXO0| title = New York Balks at Next Grand Theft Auto| author = Elizabeth Millard| publisher = NewsFactor Network| accessdate = 2015-09-08| date = 2007-04-02| 7 = | deadurl = yes| archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20141213084252/http://www.newsfactor.com/news/New-York-Balks-at-Grand-Theft-Auto/story.xhtml?story_id=0300003HXXO0| archivedate = 2014-12-13| df = }}</ref>

=== 遭法律起訴 ===
曾多次批評電子遊戲暴力內容的佛羅里達州律師[[杰克·汤普森|杰克·汤普森]]（Jack Thompson），稱會以行動去阻止[[Rockstar_Games|Rockstar]]發售遊戲。<ref>{{cite web | last = Graft | first = Kris | date = 2007-01-03 | url = http://www.next-gen.biz/index.php?option=com_content&task=view&id=4455&Itemid=2 | title = Thompson Rallies Against GTA IV | publisher = [[Future_US|Future US]] | accessdate = 2007-04-01 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20070927001223/http://www.next-gen.biz/index.php?option=com_content&task=view&id=4455&Itemid=2 | archive-date = 2007-09-27 | dead-url = no }}</ref>至2007年3月16日，[[Rockstar_Games|Rockstar]]的母公司Take Two Interactive在佛羅里達控告汤普森，試圖将汤普森阻止公司发售遊戲作品的行为定性為「{{link-en|公眾滋擾|Public nuisance}}」。于是在任务“Final Interview”中，尼克被要求去一间律师行杀掉律师，这暗示着对杰克·汤普森常常找[[Rockstar_Games|Rockstar]]公司麻烦的不满。

=== 酒後駕駛情節 ===
游戏发售后，也备受指责。一些著名的人物如{{link-en|乔治·加洛韦|George Galloway}}（George Galloway），[[杰克·汤普森|杰克·汤普森]]（Jack Thompson）和[[希拉里·克林顿|希拉里·克林顿]] 在内都批评了这个游戏，因为有机构，包括纽约市官员和“母亲反对酒后驾车”组织（Mothers Against Drunk Driving，MADD）。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.gamespot.com/articles/mothers-against-gtaivs-drunk-driving/1100-6190213/|title=Mothers against GTAIV's drunk driving|last=Sinclair|first=Brendan|date=2008-04-30|publisher=[[GameSpot|GameSpot]]|accessdate=2008-10-13|archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6YZOSNbnk?url=http://www.gamespot.com/articles/mothers-against-gtaivs-drunk-driving/1100-6190213/|archive-date=2015-05-16|dead-url=no}}</ref>MADD要求[[ESRB|ESRB]]将游戏的评级从“M”（17岁以上）提升至“AO”（Adults Only，仅限成人），因为游戏的内容包含[[酒后驾驶|酒后驾驶]]。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.madd.org/Media-Center/Media-Center/Press-Releases/Press-Releases/2008/MADD’s-Statement-Regarding-Grand-Theft-Auto-IV.aspx |title=MADD's Statement Regarding Grand Theft Auto IV |last=Tway |first=Kelley |publisher=[[Mothers_Against_Drunk_Driving|Mothers Against Drunk Driving]] |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20080513021529/http://www.madd.org/Media-Center/Media-Center/Press-Releases/Press-Releases/2008/MADD%E2%80%99s-Statement-Regarding-Grand-Theft-Auto-IV.aspx |archivedate=2008-05-13 |accessdate=2013-09-27 |deadurl=yes }}</ref>

=== 遊戲遭審查 ===
侠盗车手IV最初的版本在澳大利亚和新西兰进行预审查，让游戏来满足澳大利亚分级系统的要求。{{注|1=根据澳大利亚分级的要求，删除了血液，嫖妓的视角也发生了变化。}}<ref name="smh-censor">{{cite news |url=http://blogs.smh.com.au/screenplay/archives/017808.html |title=GTA IV edited for Australia |accessdate=2008-04-05 |last=Hill |first=Jason |date=2008-04-04 |work=The Sydney Morning Herald |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6YZOtVtE9?url=http://blogs.smh.com.au/screenplay/archives/017808.html |archive-date=2015-05-16 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>然而，本作被重新提交给{{link-en|新西兰电影与文学分级办公室|Office of Film and Literature Classification (New Zealand)}}（Office of Film and Literature Classification），原因是斯坦·加利福——一名21岁的学生的不满，新西兰因而获得了经澳大利亚法律审查过的游戏修改版本。未经修改的版本，后来被给予R18的分级并禁止在新西兰销售。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.3news.co.nz/entertainment/uncut-version-of-grand-theft-auto-iv-now-available-in-nz-2008052218 |title=Uncut version of Grand Theft Auto IV now available in NZ |work=[[3_News|3 News]] |publisher=[[MediaWorks_New_Zealand|MediaWorks]] |date=2008-05-22 |accessdate=2014-12-07 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6YZPHKvCk?url=http://www.3news.co.nz/entertainment/uncut-version-of-grand-theft-auto-iv-now-available-in-nz-2008052218 |archive-date=2015-05-16 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>对于PC版本，本作未经审查的版本在澳大利亚的分级为MA15+。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://kotaku.com/5100659/for-some-reason-australia-is-getting-an-uncut-gta-iv-on-pc |title=For Some Reason, Australia Is Getting An Uncut GTA IV On PC |last=Plunkett |first=Luke |work=[[Kotaku|Kotaku]] |publisher=[[Gawker_Media|Gawker Media]] |date=2008-12-02 |accessdate=2014-12-07 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6YZP252Um?url=http://kotaku.com/5100659/for-some-reason-australia-is-getting-an-uncut-gta-iv-on-pc |archive-date=2015-05-16 |dead-url=no }}</ref>《[[侠盗猎车手：失落与诅咒|失落与诅咒]]》发布后，Rockstar散发的游戏补丁中又有包含澳大利亚未经审查的内容。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.digitalspy.com.au/gaming/news/a147428/gta-iv-updated-with-uncensored-patch.html#~oXQMmsgdOXk9Xs |title='GTA IV' updated with uncensored patch |last=Reynolds |first=Matthew |work=[[Digital_Spy|Digital Spy]] |publisher=[[Hearst_Corporation|Hearst Corporation]] |date=2009-02-21 |accessdate=2014-12-12 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6YZP5ygEF?url=http://www.digitalspy.com.au/gaming/news/a147428/gta-iv-updated-with-uncensored-patch.html#~oXQMmsgdOXk9Xs |archive-date=2015-05-16 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

=== 衍生社會問題 ===
已经有来自英国和美国的报道因玩侠盗猎车手IV而引发的犯罪事件。<ref name="Crime incidents"/>例如，伦敦克罗伊登（Croydon）附近一个游戏店购买者受到暴力袭击，其中包括店内员工。后来据报道，虽然两群人的行为<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.mcvuk.com/news/read/croydon-stabbing-had-nothing-to-do-with-gta|title=Croydon stabbing 'had nothing to do with GTA'|last=Ingham|first=Tim|date=2008-04-30|publisher=[[Market_for_Home_Computing_and_Video_Games|Market for Home Computing and Video Games]]|accessdate=2008-11-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131022024005/http://www.mcvuk.com/news/read/croydon-stabbing-had-nothing-to-do-with-gta|archive-date=2013-10-22|dead-url=no}}</ref>与本游戏剧情无关，但还是引起了对该作的[[道德恐慌|道德恐慌]]。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.v3.co.uk/v3-uk/news/2007890/grand-theft-auto-stabbing-disputed |title=Grand Theft Auto stabbing disputed |last=Thomson |first=Iain |publisher=V3 |date=2008-04-30 |accessdate=2008-05-02 |registration=yes |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131021003030/http://www.v3.co.uk/v3-uk/news/2007890/grand-theft-auto-stabbing-disputed |archive-date=2013-10-21 |dead-url=no }}</ref>六名少年在纽约{{link-en|新海德公园|New Hyde Park, New York}}作案，对几名受害者进行袭击和抢劫，并企图劫车后于2008年6月被捕。据警方介绍，青少年声称自己是受侠盗猎车手IV的启发。<ref>{{cite news |url=http://kotaku.com/5019960/teen-crime-spree-inspired-by-grand-theft-auto |title=Teen Crime Spree Inspired By Grand Theft Auto |last=Fahey |first=Mike |work=[[Kotaku|Kotaku]] |publisher=[[Gawker_Media|Gawker Media]] |date=2008-06-26 |accessdate=2014-12-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141210210943/http://kotaku.com/5019960/teen-crime-spree-inspired-by-grand-theft-auto |archive-date=2014-12-10 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

